SEARCH
Package research

Class ResearchPaper

java.lang.Object
research.ResearchPaper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ResearchPaper extends Object implements Serializable
The ResearchPaper class represents a research paper in the system. It contains information about the paper, such as title, author, citations, annotation, keywords, section, content, date, pages, ISBN, DOI, and feedback.
